takeAny(Behaviour) - Static method in class com.android.Animal

takeMovement(Movement, Object) - Static method in class com.android.Mammal
Static method that can take a number of different Movement interface referenced object this method takes a Movement reference and an object the movement reference and the object t can only be certain combinations a Movement reference to a Mammal object, has to have a Integer sent with it * a Movement reference to a Cow object, has to have a Integer sent with it * a Movement reference to a Employee object, has to have a Dog sent with it or it can take a Lambda that implements the functional interface
